Cut audio (flac):
	ffmpeg -i input.flac -ss 00 -t 260 -c:a copy output.flac

Cut video (mkv):
	ffmpeg -i input.mkv -ss 00 -t 00:03:20 -c:v copy -c:a copy output.mkv

Convert audio:
	ffmpeg -i input.mp3 -c:a libopus -b:a 128k output.opus

Convert video (lossless):
	ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -c:v copy -c:a copy output.mkv
